# ğŸ’¡ LumiÃ¨res - Allumage (alÃ©atoire)
- alias: Simulation vacances - Allumage lumiÃ¨res (alÃ©atoire)
  description: >
    Allume les lumiÃ¨res Ã  une heure alÃ©atoire dÃ©finie dans input_datetime.lumiere_on_random uniquement
    si la simulation est active, en mode "AlÃ©atoire", et pendant la pÃ©riode de vacances.
  trigger:
    - platform: time
      at: input_datetime.lumiere_on_random
  condition:
    - condition: state
      entity_id: input_boolean.simulation_presence
      state: "on"
    - condition: state
      entity_id: input_boolean.simulation_lumieres
      state: "on"
    - condition: state
      entity_id: input_select.mode_simulation_horaires
      state: AlÃ©atoire
    - condition: template
      value_template: >
        {% set today = now().date() %}
        {% set debut = states('input_datetime.depart_vacances') %}
        {% set retour = states('input_datetime.retour_vacances') %}
        {{ debut <= today.strftime('%Y-%m-%d') <= retour }}
  action:
    - service: light.turn_on
      target:
        entity_id:
          - light.dome
          - light.spots_couleurs
          - light.eclairage_meubles_cuisine
  mode: single

